channel.title: Feel like giving up!
channel.description: im new to everything never done a private server in my life.. im wanting to create a private server i dont like 317... was wanting to do something like 508? need help have looked at tutorials downloaded clients+source but cant get them up and running :S really need help im wanting to learn please some one help me :(( if i can get the server up and running i can pretty much follow tutorials just cant get anything running!

item.title: Feel like giving up!
item.dc:creator: @masan05 masan05
item.description:
@masan05 wrote:

easy… go into your client search for 127.0.0.1, or no-ip, make sure you get the right file and right place to change, change the 127.0.0.1 to your ip.
Then go into source and search 127.0.0.1, or no-ip, same as above, change it to your ip. Save compile both the client and source, recycle the server and wala, it should work!
